info.name: YT Anxiety Blocker
info.description: After watching RTgame's video on anxiety and hearing the issue with yt basically screaming "we want you to do better", I took my little knowledge of stylus to make this. All it does it that finds the 'snapshot' panel and prevents it from rendering.

Works on https://studio.youtube.com/channel/
